-- Icelandic's Hilmarsson Discusses Yogurt, Made in U.S. (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-09-25T13:52:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-25/icelandic-s-hilmarsson-discusses-yogurt-made-in-u-s-audio-.html
Siggi Hilmarsson, founder and chief 
executive officer of Icelandic Milk and Skyr Corp., says he does
not import his product from Iceland because of cost and 
freshness considerations.  Hilmarsson talked to Bloomberg's 
Vonnie Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on  Bloomberg Radio  on 
September 24, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:44
 